Package com.vincentdao.List

Class LinkedList<T extends Comparable<T>>

java.lang.Object
com.vincentdao.List.List<T>
com.vincentdao.List.LinkedList<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
IQueue<T>, IStack<T>
public final class LinkedList<T extends Comparable<T>> extends List<T> implements IStack<T>, IQueue<T>
Implementation of the abstract class List. Contains all the methods that List offers, plus extra methods for Stack and Queue ADT.
Version:
0.1
Author:
vincentdao
